## ğŸ“Œ Overview

This Python script automatically opens the Stake daily bonus page and claims the daily bonus using **screen automation**.

It works by:

* Opening the Stake daily bonus URL in your default browser
* Navigating the page using keyboard input
* Locating the **"Claim Bonus"** button on screen via image recognition
* Clicking the button automatically
* Waiting 24 hours before repeating the process

