---

## âš™ï¸ Configuration

You can tweak these values inside the script:

| Variable             | Description                             |
| -------------------- | --------------------------------------- |
| `PAGE_LOAD_WAIT`     | Seconds to wait for page load           |
| `DAILY_WAIT`         | Time between claims (default 24h + 30s) |
| `CLAIM_BUTTON_IMAGE` | Image used for detection                |

---

## ğŸ§  How It Works

1. Opens Stake daily bonus URL
2. Waits for the page to fully load
3. Focuses the browser window
4. Uses keyboard navigation (TAB + ENTER)
5. Searches the screen for `button.png`
6. Moves the mouse smoothly and clicks
7. Starts a 24-hour countdown

---

## ğŸ›‘ Common Issues

### âŒ Button Not Found

* Retake `button.png`
* Disable browser zoom
* Ensure Stake page is visible on screen

### âŒ PyAutoGUI Display Errors

* Run on **Windows Python**, not WSL
* Ensure a monitor is connected

---

## ğŸ”’ Safety Tips

* Do not move your mouse while script runs
* Do not minimize the browser
* Run when the computer will stay unlocked
* Consider running once per day instead of looping

